collectionMetadata.name: Number of Dentists and Oral Health Therapists
collectionMetadata.description:
Number of Dentists (Dental Specialist, General Dental Practitioners) and Oral Health Therapists by sector (Public, Private, Not in Active Practice). 

"Dentists" include those from Division I and II under the Singapore Dental Council. 

Registration of Oral Health Therapists started in 2008.

datasetMetadata.name: Number of Dentists
datasetMetadata.description:
Number of Dentists (Dental Specialist, General Dental Practitioners/Public, Private, Not in Active Practice). 
Dentists refer to Division I and II dentists.

datasetMetadata.name: Number of Oral Health Therapists
datasetMetadata.description:
Number of Oral Health Therapists (Public, Private, Not in Active Practice). 
Registration of Oral Health Therapists started in 2008.
